description:
Do you feel overwhelmed by the prospect of having to find a new software
engineering job because you dread the technical interviewing process?
Have you been putting off submitting your job applications because you
think you won't be ready to interview until you do "just one more" day
of studying?

In this talk, you'll learn which concepts are the most important to
study for entry-level roles and how to use your Python skills to convey
your understanding of these concepts with confidence and clarity.
title: Ace Your Technical Interview Using Python
